OL,3,CNew hotel brings accommodation record
OL,4,Cin NI
OL,6,FThe opening of a new hotel in Belfast
OL,7,FCity Centre has helped the industry
OL,8,Fsurpass the 10,000 room mark across
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FJanice Gault, Chief Executive, NI
OL,12,FHotels Federation said: "I think
OL,13,Ftourism is really about regeneration.
OL,14,FWe've seen a lot of old buildings
OL,15,Fbeing brought back to life over the
OL,16,Fyears, and a lot of new builds go into
OL,17,Fsites which were previously not being
OL,18,Fused particularly well."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
