OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775718328
OL,3,CNew hotel brings accommodation record
OL,4,Cin NI
OL,6,FShe continued: "I think the investment
OL,7,Fthat the industry has made, about 1.7
OL,8,Fbillion over the last probably two
OL,9,Fdecades, it's really good to see that
OL,10,Finvestment in this as a destination.
OL,12,F"We've the opportunity to deliver
OL,13,Fjobs, not only in cities but
OL,14,Fthroughout Northern Ireland, and I
OL,15,Fthink that's an important thing about
OL,16,Fthe tourism industry.
OL,18,F"Not only is there a product for
OL,19,Feverybody, there's quite often a job
OL,20,Ffor everybody within the industry."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
