OL,3,CNew hotel brings accommodation record
OL,4,Cin NI
OL,6,FA ribbon-cutting ceremony marked the
OL,7,Fofficial opening of The Bedford on
OL,8,FWednesday.
OL,10,FThe formerly vacant Scottish Provident
OL,11,Fpremises, on the corner of Bedford
OL,12,FStreet and Howard Street has been
OL,13,Fbrought back to life as an 82 bed
OL,14,Fboutique hotel steeped in local
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,FMany of the original features in the
OL,18,FGrade B listed building have been
OL,19,Fpreserved including original vault
OL,20,Fdoors scattered throughout the
OL,21,Fpremises.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
