FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775718328
OL,3,CNew hotel brings accommodation record
OL,4,Cin NI
OL,6,FMatt Gatt, General Manager of the
OL,7,FBedford said that "Northern Ireland,
OL,8,Fand particularly Belfast, is a growing
OL,9,Fdestination for national and
OL,10,Finternational travellers. So, we think
OL,11,Fthat we're bringing this hotel, this
OL,12,Fbeautiful hotel, to the marketplace at
OL,13,Fthe right time."
OL,15,FAs Belfast's accommodation sector
OL,16,Fexpands, the demand has risen for new
OL,17,Fconcepts, like the Well aparthotel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
