PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775718328
OL,3,CNew hotel brings accommodation record
OL,4,Cin NI
OL,6,FAlastair Coulson, Managing Director,
OL,7,FLotus Property said: "Apart-hotels, I
OL,8,Fsuppose, is the best of both worlds.
OL,9,FYou know, you've got the functionality
OL,10,Fand services of a hotel, and then
OL,11,Fyou've got the flexibility.
OL,13,F"Every room has its own kitchen, a
OL,14,Fliving room, and somewhere to sleep."
OL,16,FHe continued: "I think Belfast has a
OL,17,Fgrowing tourism and business economy,
OL,18,Fand the apart-hotel is quite young in
OL,19,Fthe city."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
