OL,3,CNew hotel brings accommodation record
OL,4,Cin NI
OL,6,FThe Well is expected to be open for
OL,7,Fbusiness next May. Alongside the
OL,8,FBedford Hotel and other projects, they
OL,9,Fserve to highlight the growing
OL,10,Finterest in Northern Ireland as a
OL,11,Ftourist destination.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
